your authority over the family.

00:15:35.962 --> 00:15:37.082
No wonder.

00:15:38.100 --> 00:15:40.880
They searched everywhere but couldn't
find the Xiao family's private seal.

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:43.780
It was hidden in this hairpin all along.

00:15:45.300 --> 00:15:46.540
Your Lordship,

00:15:48.100 --> 00:15:49.380
now,

00:15:49.980 --> 00:15:52.020
are you willing to raise an army?

